1.0c little speedup, 5 august, 2005
1.1  bugfix: SimpleView don't freeze anymore if file was no picture, 5 august, 2005
1.1b bugfix: some (little) pictures fits now exactly, 25 august, 2005
1.4 SimpleView_WB: add "PDTA_DestMode,PMODE_V43" for more stability with especially
    8bit pictures as GIF, removed a not needed branch.
    SimpleView for pictures on an own (24bit) screen added, 26 april 2006
1.5 SimpleView bugfix: a 650 × 1297 image comes now on best screen, BestModeID improved.
1.6 SimpleView bugfix: other programms can load the picture.
    SimpleView improvement: write from scratch the picture shown routines, 8bit picture
    pen color converting own (fast) routine.
1.6b SimpleView bugfix: slowsdown/freezes because code meant for 8bit pictures was
    executed for 24bit pictures too.
    SimpleView improvement: added branch prediction that was forgotten. 20 may 2006
1.6c SimpleView speedup, pictures with depth <=8bit, 3 instead of 4 bytes converting/displaying.
1.6d SimpleView little speedup, rearranged code in 8bit pictures part, removed one commandline. 30may06
1.6e SimpleView little speedup. 1 june 2006
1.6f SimpleView little speedup, 68 bytes shorter ! 5 june 2006
1.6g SimpleView improved loop in 8bit part.
1.7 SimpleView added scaledown pictures to fit on biggest screen
