1.8 SimpleView truly simplerefresh window now, pressing "Q" or "Esc" keys to quits. closing code at end now,
    where it's belongs. 30 nov 2006
1.8b SimpleView little speedups, SimpleView is a public screen. 4 dec 2006
1.8f SimpleView programming more stable IDCMP's handling, filesize shorter 29 dec 2006
